data.description: Discover your dream mountain retreat with this exceptional 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom light fixer-upper, nestled on a picturesque 2.86-acre lot. This two-story log home boasts winter views of the distant valley and features a partially finished basement wired and plumbed for an additional bedroom and bath. Immerse yourself in the warmth of wood-faced walls and hardwood flooring throughout, complemented by a stunning cathedral ceiling and a captivating stacked stone fireplace in the living area. The open kitchen flows seamlessly into the dining and living spaces, creating an inviting atmosphere for entertaining. The master bedroom on the main floor includes a spacious bath with his and her vanities, a separate shower, and a luxurious garden tub. Enjoy the scenic surroundings from the wrap-around porch or the loft overlooking the living area. Complete with an attached triple garage and a sizable concrete parking area, this mountain haven is not only perfect for everyday living but also presents a fantastic opportunity for a weekend getaway or a lucrative short-term rental. Donat miss out a see private remarks for showing and offer instructions. Your mountain paradise awaits! NOTE: Principals of the seller may share ownership in a licensed real estate brokerage.
